(7366, 3, '2015-11-18 08:37:53', '2015-11-18 08:37:53', '[cmsmasters_row data_padding_bottom="0" data_padding_top="0" data_color="default" data_width="boxed"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/1"][cmsmasters_slider slider_plugin="layer" slider_layer="1"][cmsmasters_featured_block text_width="100" text_position="center" text_align="center" fb_bg_color="#de9f2c" top_padding="3" bottom_padding="3" bd_width="0" animation_delay="0" classes="cmsmasters_home_fb_construct"]<span style="font-family: open sans; font-size: 16pt; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff;">EN MACROMAD ESTAMOS LISTOS PARA AYUDARTE!</span>[/cmsmasters_featured_block][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_classes="cmsmasters_home_icons_styles" data_padding_bottom="130" data_padding_top="110" data_color="default" data_width="boxed"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/4"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Atención personalizada" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-flag-4" box_icon_size="60" box_icon_space="15" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="0%" box_icon_color="rgba(243,193,75,0.6)" box_icon_bg_color="#ffffff" box_icon_bd_color="#ffffff" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 43px;">Nos caracterizamos por tener la mejor atención personalizada.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/4"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Somos líderes" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-home-3" box_icon_size="60" box_icon_space="15" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="0%" box_icon_color="rgba(243,193,75,0.6)" box_icon_bg_color="#ffffff" box_icon_bd_color="#ffffff" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 43px;">Somos líderes en calidad y variedad. En Macromad encontrá todo para concretar tus proyectos.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/4"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Servicio integral" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-ok-1" box_icon_size="60" box_icon_space="15" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="0%" box_icon_color="rgba(243,193,75,0.6)" box_icon_bg_color="#ffffff" box_icon_bd_color="#ffffff" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 43px;">Vení, consultá, comprá y empezá a trabajar.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/4"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Asesoramiento gratuito" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-settings" box_icon_size="60" box_icon_space="15" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="0%" box_icon_color="rgba(243,193,75,0.6)" box_icon_bg_color="#ffffff" box_icon_bd_color="#ffffff" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 43px;">Te brindamos todas las opciones y soluciones que necesitás.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_width="boxed" data_top_style="default" data_bot_style="default" data_color="second" data_bg_color="#3d3d3d" data_padding_top="0" data_padding_bottom="15" data_classes="cmsmasters_home_portfolio_m"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/3"][cmsmasters_image align="center" animation_delay="0"]10745|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/01-300x169.png|medium[/cmsmasters_image][cmsmasters_heading type="h4" font_weight="bold" font_style="normal" text_align="center" margin_top="30" margin_bottom="30" animation_delay="0"]Accesorios[/cmsmasters_heading][cmsmasters_text animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">En Macromad encontrarás todos los accesorios que necesitas.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_text][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/3"][cmsmasters_image align="center" animation_delay="0"]10746|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/02-300x169.png|medium[/cmsmasters_image][cmsmasters_heading type="h4" font_weight="bold" font_style="normal" text_align="center" margin_top="30" margin_bottom="30" animation_delay="0"]Maderas[/cmsmasters_heading][cmsmasters_text animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Defendemos los bosques y trabajamos junto a proveedores avalados por la FSC.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_text][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/3"][cmsmasters_image align="center" animation_delay="0"]10747|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/03-300x169.png|medium[/cmsmasters_image][cmsmasters_heading type="h4" font_weight="bold" font_style="normal" text_align="center" margin_top="30" margin_bottom="30" animation_delay="0"]Herramientas[/cmsmasters_heading][cmsmasters_text animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Trabajamos con las marcas líderes del mercado. Calidad, variedad y garantía.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_text][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_padding_bottom="90" data_padding_top="90" data_color="default" data_width="boxed"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/2" data_classes="cmsmasters_homepage_contact_form"][cmsmasters_featured_block text_width="92" text_position="center" text_align="left" fb_bg_color="#f3f3f3" bg_img="10787|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Macromad-web_slide-06-202x300.png|medium" bg_position="bottom right" bg_repeat="no-repeat" bg_attachment="scroll" bg_size="auto" top_padding="39" bottom_padding="50" bd_color="#f9f9f9" bd_width="10" animation_delay="0"]\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 800;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">SOLICITAR COTIZACIÓN</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">Comunicate con nosotros y obtené un presupuesto a la brevedad.</span>\r\n\r\n[cmsmasters_divider width="long" height="0" style="solid" position="center" margin_top="30" animation_delay="0"][cmsmasters_contact_form form_plugin="cfb" form_cfb="9887" email_cfb="#" animation_delay="0"]\r\n\r\n[/cmsmasters_featured_block][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/2"][cmsmasters_heading type="h3" font_size="20" line_height="28" font_weight="900" font_style="normal" text_align="left" margin_top="15" margin_bottom="5" animation_delay="0"]¿Que dicen nuestros clientes?[/cmsmasters_heading][cmsmasters_quotes mode="grid" columns="1" animation_delay="0"][cmsmasters_quote image="10841|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/04-50x50_02.png|full" name="Juan Pablo Ferrari" subtitle="Carpintero"]\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: open sans; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 600; color: #535353;">Las mejores herramientas!</span>\r\n\r\n[cmsmasters_divider width="long" height="0" style="solid" position="center" margin_top="10" animation_delay="0"]\r\n\r\nSi sos un profesional de la carpintería, te va a encantar!. Las mejores herramientas a un precio muy conveniente, super recomendable!\r\n\r\n[/cmsmasters_quote][cmsmasters_quote image="10842|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/04-50x50_01.png|full" name="Martina Urruti Rozina" subtitle="Arquitecta"]\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: open sans; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: 600; color: #535353;">La mejor atención!</span>\r\n\r\n[cmsmasters_divider width="long" height="0" style="solid" position="center" margin_top="10" animation_delay="0"]\r\n\r\nEl asesoramiento de Macromad es fundamental cuando se tratan de nuevos proyectos. 100% recomendable!\r\n\r\n[/cmsmasters_quote][/cmsmasters_quotes][cmsmasters_divider width="long" height="0" style="solid" position="center" margin_top="-30" margin_bottom="-30" animation_delay="0"][cmsmasters_button button_link="http://construction-pro.cmsmasters.net/contact-us/" button_target="self" button_text_align="right" button_font_family="Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,600,600italic,700,700italic,800,800italic" button_font_size="13" button_line_height="13" button_font_weight="bol