ounter subtitle="Tu proyecto, es nuestro compromiso" value="100" value_suffix="%" icon_type="icon"]Comprometidos[/cmsmasters_counter][/cmsmasters_counters][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_padding_bottom="0" data_padding_top="80" data_color="default" data_bot_style="default" data_top_style="default" data_width="boxed"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/2"][cmsmasters_heading type="h1" font_size="28" font_weight="900" font_style="normal" text_align="left" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="20" animation_delay="0"]Quienes somos[/cmsmasters_heading][cmsmasters_image align="none" animation_delay="0"]9729|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/red-line.png|full[/cmsmasters_image][cmsmasters_divider width="long" height="0" style="solid" position="center" margin_top="0" margin_bottom="50" animation_delay="0"][cmsmasters_text animation_delay="0"]<span style="font-size: 14pt;">Con más de 30 años de trayectoria sumado a una visión contemporánea, nace MACROMAD. Conocemos el rubro desde hace mucho tiempo y sabemos que somos distribuidores de la mejor calidad en maderas e insumos en Tucumán.</span>[/cmsmasters_text][cmsmasters_divider width="long" height="0" style="solid" position="center" margin_top="30" margin_bottom="0" animation_delay="0"][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/2"][cmsmasters_gallery layout="slider" image_size_slider="full" slider_effect="slide" slider_autoplay="true" slider_slideshow_speed="7" slider_animation_speed="600" slider_pause_on_hover="true" slider_rewind="true" slider_rewind_speed="1000" slider_nav_arrow="true" animation_delay="0"]10851|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/02_j-150x150.png,10852|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/02_i-150x150.png,10853|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/02_k-150x150.png[/cmsmasters_gallery][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_width="boxed" data_no_margin="true" data_top_style="default" data_bot_style="default" data_color="default" data_padding_top="10" data_padding_bottom="10"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/1"][cmsmasters_text animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Servicios: Brindamos una atención personalizada, atendemos las inquietudes de nuestros clientes ofreciéndoles una amplia variedad de productos. Juntos elegimos los productos que sean acordes a sus necesidades. En MACROMAD no te vas sin una solución.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_text][cmsmasters_gallery layout="slider" image_size_slider="full" slider_effect="slide" slider_autoplay="true" slider_slideshow_speed="7" slider_animation_speed="600" slider_pause_on_hover="true" slider_rewind="true" slider_rewind_speed="1000" slider_nav_arrow="true" animation_delay="0"]10857|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/02-1-150x150.png,10858|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/02_c-1-150x150.png,10859|http://www.macromad.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/02_b-1-150x150.png[/cmsmasters_gallery][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_padding_bottom="30" data_padding_top="70" data_bg_color="#f1f1f1" data_color="default" data_width="boxed"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/3"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Integridad profesional" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-user-1" box_icon_size="30" box_icon_space="50" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="50%" box_icon_color="#f3c14b" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 71px;">Estamos comprometidos con nuestros clientes, pero sobre todo con nuestros empleados. Nos aseguramos de que reciban una capacitación adecuada para poder brindar un excelente servicio.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/3"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Trabajo en equipo" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-rocket" box_icon_size="30" box_icon_space="50" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="50%" box_icon_color="#f3c14b" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 71px;">En macromad nos gusta comprometernos con sus proyectos, es por eso que le ofrecemos un trabajo en equipo durante el desarrollo de su proyecto.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/3"][cmsmasters_icon_box box_type="cmsmasters_icon_heading_left" title="Green Friendly" heading_type="h3" box_icon_type="icon" box_icon="cmsmasters-icon-leaf-1" box_icon_size="30" box_icon_space="50" box_icon_border_width="0" box_icon_border_radius="50%" box_icon_color="#f3c14b" box_border_width="0" animation_delay="0"]\r\n<p style="padding-left: 71px;">Porque el medio ambiente es lo más importante para nosotros, trabajamos con madera certificada por IFS, la cuales provienen exclusivamente de bosques sembrados.</p>\r\n[/cmsmasters_icon_box][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row][cmsmasters_row data_width="boxed" data_color="default" data_bg_color="#3d3d3d" data_padding_top="0" data_padding_bottom="0"][cmsmasters_column data_width="1/1"][cmsmasters_clients columns="5" layout="slider" height="90" autoplay="true" animation_delay="0"][cmsmasters_client logo="9746|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/renovate-solutions1.png|full" link="#"]Renovate Solutions[/cmsmasters_client][cmsmasters_client logo="9747|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/toolbox1.png|full" link="#"]Toolbox[/cmsmasters_client][cmsmasters_client logo="9748|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/architect1.png|full" link="#"]Architect[/cmsmasters_client][cmsmasters_client logo="9749|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/power-max1.png|full" link="#"]Power Max[/cmsmasters_client][cmsmasters_client logo="9750|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/building-construction1.png|full" link="#"]Building Construction[/cmsmasters_client][cmsmasters_client logo="10271|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/super-builders1.png|full" link="#"]Super Builders[/cmsmasters_client][cmsmasters_client logo="10270|http://localhost/macromadnueva/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/high-constructions1.png|full" link="#"]High Constructions[/cmsmasters_client][/cmsmasters_clients][/cmsmasters_column][/cmsmasters_row]', 'Sobre nosotros', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '529-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-23 20:17:50', '2016-08-23 23:17:50', '', 529, 'http://localhost/macromad/529-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
